OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FThe prime minister is reportedly
OL,7,Fexpected to include the security
OL,8,Fservices within the Hillsborough Law,
OL,9,Fcreating a 'duty of candour' for
OL,10,Fpublic authorities to co-operate with
OL,11,Fdisaster inquiries.
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer is expected to scrap
OL,14,Finitial plan that would have given
OL,15,Fsecurity services an exemption from
OL,16,Fthe law.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FAsked on Monday about whether he would
OL,7,Fdeliver on his promise to get the Bill
OL,8,Fpassed, Sir Keir told reporters: "I
OL,9,Fdid make that promise and I intend to
OL,10,Fdeliver on that promise."
OL,12,FLast year, an amendment was pulled at
OL,13,Fthe eleventh hour over concerns that
OL,14,Fintelligence agencies could use it to
OL,15,Favoid being bound by the proposed duty
OL,16,Fof candour, but ministers are now
OL,17,Fexpected to ensure security chiefs
OL,18,Fwill not be able to veto spies from
OL,19,Fgiving evidence.
OL,26,@pD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FFirst reported by The Times, security
OL,7,Fchiefs will not be allowed to block
OL,8,Fspies, and will have to make a court
OL,9,Fapplication for disclosures to be
OL,10,Fpartially or fully exempted.
OL,12,FWhen asked whether the security
OL,13,Fservices would be included in the duty
OL,14,Fof candour, the PM said: "We've been
OL,15,Ftalking to the families and others
OL,16,Fabout how we get that right... we'll
OL,17,Fcontinue with that work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,F"I want to make sure this is right,
OL,7,Fbut this week on the anniversary, the
OL,8,Fannual reminder, it is important to go
OL,9,Fback to the human element here."
OL,11,FWednesday 15 April will mark the 37th
OL,12,Fanniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,13,Fdisaster.
OL,15,FThe Labour Government proposed a duty
OL,16,Fof candour as part of the Public
OL,17,FOffice (Accountability) Bill - also
OL,18,Fknown as the Hillsborough Law - to
OL,19,Fmeet a manifesto pledge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FThe campaigners say the bill's delay
OL,7,Fhas undermined their trust in the
OL,8,FGovernment, and has had a "serious,
OL,9,Fnegative impact on countless families."
OL,11,FThe PM said: "This week is obviously
OL,12,Fan important week because it's the
OL,13,Fanniversary ` anniversary seems the
OL,14,Fwrong word in a way ` but it's the
OL,15,Fyearly reminder of what happened and
OL,16,Fthe pain the families have gone
OL,17,Fthrough, are still going through, and
OL,18,Fthe injustice that was inflicted on
OL,19,Fthem for many, many years."
OL,26,@sD@NOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FHe continued: "I intend to make good
OL,7,Fon the promise that I made. Obviously
OL,8,Fwe're working with the families and
OL,9,Fothers on the final balance that we
OL,10,Fneed to get right in the proposed
OL,11,Flegislation.
OL,13,F"But the duty of candour, the duty,
OL,14,Fbasically, that public officials need
OL,15,Fto come forward and tell the truth `
OL,16,Fthat's a really important principle
OL,17,Fthat drives me.
OL,26,@nD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776153957
OL,3,CSecurity service expected to 'not be
OL,4,Cexempt' from Hillsborough Law
OL,6,F"So, we'll keep working on this, it's
OL,7,Fimportant to get it right... I've made
OL,8,Fa promise and I intend to act on that
OL,9,Fpromise."
OL,11,FThe proposed legislation takes its
OL,12,Fname from the Hillsborough disaster,
OL,13,Fafter which families campaigned for
OL,14,Fyears to get to the truth behind what
OL,15,Fcaused the crush which led to the
OL,16,Fdeath of 97 football fans at the FA
OL,17,FCup semi-final between Liverpool and
OL,18,FNottingham Forest in 1989.
OL,26,@qD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
